02:24:57.000 --> 02:25:18.000
So I think that's, I want to just say a few things. It may take a few minutes, but so I think it will provide many things. It will provide a kind of structure, philosophical framework, a sense of a tradition through which we can re-experience something very beautiful.

02:25:19.000 --> 02:25:28.000
Beautiful good and true in my view, which is what the greatest art of our civilization has produced.

02:25:29.000 --> 02:25:40.000
